@Node 2 "Ed."

So what is this? Edition 1.5? Newsflash? What are we talking about. There
has been a problem you se with the first edition of 'The Cracked Regular'!
This is quite a big problem as it has infected a loth of the other "products"
which we have released.

You can read more about it in @{"'The Problem'!" link 3} But in general it is that we
have written the wrong e.mail address in our products!!! This I have just
found out right after I uploaded all of our stuff to Aminet. I have fixed
some of it by rewriting to netshort file. But this is not enough. And someone
has had to have got the wrong address! That is why I have decided to release
this 1.5 NEWSFLASH ed. For those who won't read this, shit au!!!

There has been some internal badgering in E.R.S.98 to. Don't get gossipy
now. We do not have internal conflicts. Okay, E.R.S.98's members are not the
most active members, but that is not the point. As E.R.S.98 was founded by
Sorg to a media to release stuff to other people, other members are not
obliged to do anything, and most often they don't do very much. I have to
do most of the work myself but my intention was never anything else.
E.R.S.98 are a gang of "amateur" artist who do what they want to do!

